extensions.name: IPAM Security Policy App
extensions.description: The Tufin IPAM sync app integrates Tufin SecureTrack with IP Address Management systems to populate networks zones in order to use the USP in SecureTrack.

extensions.name: SecureTrack Reporting Essentials
extensions.description: The SecureTrack Reporting Essentials (STRE) is a Marketplace application for generating a wide-variety of operational-reports based on SecureTrack data in a format that is easily read and understood.

extensions.name: Vulnerability Mitigation App
extensions.description: The Tufin Vulnerability Mitigation app (VMA) enables Tufin customers to prioritize remediation and mitigation efforts by enhancing vulnerability scanner output with network insights.
